entries.femaleVariant: Have you tried seeking professional help, ma'am?
No, ma'am... I mean an electrician – it could just be voltage fluctuations.
Voltage fluctuations don't try to murder you in your sleep!
I'm telling the truth – my appliances are possessed!
The lights flicker on and off, the T.V. changes channels by itself, and the thermostat – don't get me started on the thermostat!
Right, OK... Well in that case I'd go with incense. You have to fumigate all your electrical appliances three times a day.
Oh, five times for the thermostat, minimum.
